Minimal README for dyndnsc
--------------------------
Installation is done using distutils: http://docs.python.org/distutils/

E.g. running
 
  # python setup.py install
  
should be sufficient to install the dyndnsc client module.

Alternatively, you can use setuptools from http://peak.telecommunity.com/DevCenter/setuptools
to install the newest version from the internet:

  # easy_install dyndnsc

Licensing is documented in the file COPYING.

The API documentation can be viewed using `pydoc` and is found inline in the
code.